title: Delavan Christian Reformed Church

review.description: A wonderful place to worship and praise God for all of his blessings to us. A church that is committed to The infallible Word of God, Christ as the Lord of our lives and a life of gratitude...
What a wonderful community of believers! Living, loving and learning together--DCRC is a true family striving to be the hands and feet of Jesus.
